# Traverum Monorepo

## Project Overview
Traverum is a white-label booking platform that transforms hotels into "Destination Hubs" by enabling them to sell local experiences.

## Repository Structure
- apps/widget - Next.js 14 customer-facing booking widget (book.traverum.com)
- apps/dashboard - Vite+React supplier dashboard (dashboard.traverum.com)  
- packages/shared - Shared TypeScript types and utilities

## Tech Stack
- Payments: Stripe Connect
- Database: Supabase (PostgreSQL)

